在下载被人项目后 npm install下，node-sass下载失败，



提示
Downloading binary from https://github.com/sass/node-sass/releases/download/v4.7.2/linux-x64-51_binding.node
Cannot download "https://github.com/sass/node-sass/releases/download/v4.7.2/linux-x64-51_binding.node": 

ESOCKETTIMEDOUT

Hint: If github.com is not accessible in your location
      try setting a proxy via HTTP_PROXY, e.g. 

      export HTTP_PROXY=http://example.com:1234

or configure npm proxy via

      npm config set proxy http://example.com:8080


转用淘宝镜像


npm install node-sass --registry=http://registry.npm.taobao.org